<font color="#ffff00">Mother Mildred</font>
<font color="#ffff00">was anxious that she should</font>

11:57.960 --> 11:59.240
<font color="#ffff00">gain experience.</font>

11:59.240 --> 12:01.440
<font color="#ffffff">And why should that be</font>
<font color="#ffffff">at our expense?</font>

12:01.440 --> 12:04.880
<font color="#ffffff">She can't go out unsupervised</font>
<font color="#ffffff">until further notice.</font>

12:04.880 --> 12:08.440
<font color="#ffffff">She's a dead leg,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">not an extra pair of hands.</font>

12:09.840 --> 12:12.160
<font color="#ffffff">PAINED GROANS</font>

12:12.160 --> 12:14.640
<font color="#00ff00">Boss let me off early, Les.</font>

12:14.640 --> 12:17.600
<font color="#ffffff">GROANS INTENSIFY</font>
<font color="#00ff00">It sounds like it's killing her!</font>

12:21.000 --> 12:22.960
<font color="#00ff00">I thought you were meant</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to be helping!</font>

12:22.960 --> 12:24.720
<font color="#00ffff">The midwife won't let me in!</font>

12:24.720 --> 12:26.200
<font color="#00ffff">My stomach's off.</font>

12:27.680 --> 12:29.080
<font color="#00ff00">Lel!</font>

12:29.080 --> 12:30.400
<font color="#00ff00">Lesley...</font>

12:34.240 --> 12:36.720
<font color="#ffffff">What do you do for</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a living, Mr Whyte?</font>

12:36.720 --> 12:38.120
<font color="#00ff00">I'm a gas fitter.</font>

12:38.120 --> 12:40.160
<font color="#ffffff">In which case, we're halfway there.</font>

12:52.000 --> 12:54.240
<font color="#ffffff">You take a little rest now,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">precious.</font>

12:54.240 --> 12:56.000
<font color="#ffffff">Breathe in some nice, cool, air.</font>

12:56.000 --> 12:58.080
<font color="#00ff00">Can I watch it being born?</font>

12:58.080 --> 12:59.320
<font color="#00ff00">Can I see it coming out?</font>

12:59.320 --> 13:01.960
<font color="#ffffff">You're doing just fine</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with that gas mask, Mr Whyte.</font>

13:01.960 --> 13:04.680
<font color="#ffffff">I wouldn't get over ambitious.</font>

13:08.040 --> 13:09.280
<font color="#ffffff">Push...</font>

13:10.240 --> 13:12.240
<font color="#ffffff">Another one. </font><font color="#00ff00">Come on, girl!</font>

13:12.240 --> 13:14.880
<font color="#00ff00">Come on! You can do it.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">You can do it, come on!</font>

13:19.680 --> 13:21.480
<font color="#ffffff">That's it, precious!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Don't hold back!</font>

13:21.480 --> 13:24.720
<font color="#ffffff">You push, you push</font>
<font color="#ffffff">like the courageous girl you are!</font>

13:27.120 --> 13:28.880
<font color="#ffffff">Oh!</font>

13:32.600 --> 13:34.480
<font color="#ffffff">BABY CRIES</font>

13:39.120 --> 13:41.560
<font color="#ffffff">A beautiful boy!</font>

13:41.560 --> 13:44.160
<font color="#ffffff">Wasn't that worth all the pain?</font>

13:44.160 --> 13:47.120
<font color="#ffff00">I'd do it again tomorrow!</font>

13:47.120 --> 13:49.560
<font color="#ffff00">Not without the gas, though.</font>

13:50.920 --> 13:52.520
<font color="#00ff00">I'm so proud of you.</font>

13:53.560 --> 13:56.960
<font color="#ffffff">OK, you, we've still got</font>
<font color="#ffffff">some work to do.</font>

14:14.080 --> 14:16.760
<font color="#ffffff">SHE COUGHS</font>

14:16.760 --> 14:20.480
<font color="#ffff00">You...you should not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">dispose of these.</font>

14:20.480 --> 14:23.160
<font color="#ffff00">They are the cornerstones</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of our trade...</font>

14:24.640 --> 14:28.960
<font color="#ffff00">..and their work is no nearer</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to completion than our own.</font>

14:28.960 --> 14:30.200
<font color="#00ffff">Nurse Crane says otherwise,</font>

14:30.200 --> 14:32.520
<font color="#00ffff">and you know what she's like</font>
<font color="#00ffff">when she digs her heels in.</font>

14:32.520 --> 14:36.120
<font color="#ffff00">I hope that,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">when our own use is concluded,</font>

14:36.120 --> 14:40.000
<font color="#ffff00">we are not all faced</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with cremation in a dustbin!</font>

14:43.200 --> 14:45.040
<font color="#ffffff">SHE COUGHS</font>

14:48.280 --> 14:51.760
<font color="#ffffff">KNOCK ON DOOR</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Morning, Mrs Whyte.</font>

14:51.760 --> 14:53.440
<font color="#ffffff">Midwife calling!</font>

14:55.800 --> 14:58.240
<font color="#ffffff">I brought Sister Frances with me.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">She's new.</font>

14:58.240 --> 15:00.200
<font color="#00ff00">I've never been in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a tower block before.</font>

15:00.200 --> 15:02.680
<font color="#00ff00">It's quite exciting. </font><font color="#00ffff">Please.</font>

15:04.480 --> 15:06.520
<font color="#00ffff">I'll make a pot of tea.</font>

15:06.520 --> 15:08.600
<font color="#ffffff">Good morning, precious. How are you?</font>

15:08.600 --> 15:10.000
<font color="#00ff00">Morning, Mrs Whyte.</font>

15:22.280 --> 15:23.600
<font color="#ffff00">Excuse me!</font>

15:25.280 --> 15:27.880
<font color="#ffffff">Hello. </font><font color="#ffff00">Excuse me!</font>

15:30.280 --> 15:33.560
<font color="#ffff00">Margaret,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you've got to come in here!</font>

15:33.560 --> 15:35.200
<font color="#ffff00">You should never have left me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with them.</font>

15:35.200 --> 15:37.720
<font color="#ffffff">I was doing my sample,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">it's not a spectator sport.</font>

15:37.720 --> 15:39.360
<font color="#ffffff">Anyway, they needed to go</font>
<font color="#ffffff">themselves.</font>

15:39.360 --> 15:41.000
<font color="#ffff00">Yeah, well,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Kenny never made it in time</font>

15:41.000 --> 15:42.600
<font color="#ffff00">and now his trousers</font>
<font color="#ffff00">are sopping wet.</font>

15:42.600 --> 15:44.400
<font color="#ffff00">There's a ruddy great puddle</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on the floor.</font>

15:44.400 --> 15:47.120
<font color="#ffff00">I had to take the roller towel down</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to clean him up.</font>

15:47.120 --> 15:49.000
<font color="#ffff00">I love them.</font>

15:49.000 --> 15:51.880
<font color="#ffff00">But I could swing for them!</font>

15:51.880 --> 15:55.080
<font color="#ffffff">Do you know what, Clark Lombardi?</font>

15:55.080 --> 15:56.520
<font color="#ffffff">I could say the same to you.</font>

16:01.160 --> 16:03.640
<font color="#00ffff">The most important thing to remember</font>

16:03.640 --> 16:06.360
<font color="#00ffff">is that this is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a much less formal space</font>

16:06.360 --> 16:07.680
<font color="#00ffff">than the surgery.</font>

16:07.680 --> 16:10.480
<font color="#00ffff">But the same rules</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of confidentiality,</font>

16:10.480 --> 16:13.920
<font color="#00ffff">respect and patient dignity apply.</font>

16:13.920 --> 16:16.400
<font color="#ffff00">And here comes Mrs Lombardi.</font>

16:16.400 --> 16:19.400
<font color="#ffff00">Stately as a galleon</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as she sails across the floor.</font>

16:19.400 --> 16:21.000
<font color="#ffffff">Ha-bloomin'-ha.</font>

16:21.000 --> 16:23.800
<font color="#ffff00">We think of you as one</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of our star patients.</font>

16:23.800 --> 16:27.480
<font color="#ffff00">Not many cases of twins</font>
<font color="#ffff00">are diagnosed in utero.</font>

16:27.480 --> 16:31.000
<font color="#ffff00">Dr Turner and the midwives</font>
<font color="#ffff00">usually miss them.</font>

16:31.000 --> 16:33.720
<font color="#00ffff">Why don't you come straight through</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to the cubicle with me,</font>

16:33.720 --> 16:35.240
<font color="#00ffff">Mrs Lombardi?</font>

16:35.240 --> 16:39.040
<font color="#00ffff">We can catch up</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with the weighing-in queue later.</font>

16:39.040 --> 16:40.800
<font color="#ffffff">I never wanted any more.</font>

16:40.800 --> 16:42.640
<font color="#ffffff">Two was enough,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for me and me other half.</font>

16:42.640 --> 16:45.280
<font color="#ffffff">And now we're doubling</font>
<font color="#ffffff">our family in one go.</font>

16:45.280 --> 16:47.240
<font color="#00ffff">Is your husband a help</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with the little ones,</font>

16:47.240 --> 16:48.280
<font color="#00ffff">Mrs Lombardi?</font>

16:48.280 --> 16:52.840
<font color="#ffffff">He won't wipe their noses,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">never mind their backsides.</font>

16:52.840 --> 16:56.000
<font color="#ffffff">It's like when he realises</font>
<font color="#ffffff">they're people, not play things,</font>

16:56.000 --> 16:57.640
<font color="#ffffff">they frighten him.</font>

16:57.640 --> 16:58.960
<font color="#00ffff">What about rest?</font>

16:58.960 --> 17:00.840
<font color="#00ffff">Are you managing to get any sleep?</font>

17:01.880 --> 17:03.600
<font color="#ffffff">I can't get comfy lying down.</font>

17:05.880 --> 17:09.119
<font color="#ffffff">And I can't even sleep sitting up,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">cos of my bleeding piles!</font>

17:09.119 --> 17:11.720
<font color="#ffffff">The ointment</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the doctor gave me's useless!</font>

17:11.720 --> 17:14.800
<font color="#00ffff">Let's do your checks,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">then we'll get him to look at you.</font>

17:31.680 --> 17:35.320
<font color="#ffff00">Have you tried applying an ice pack,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Mrs Lombardi?</font>

17:35.320 --> 17:38.120
<font color="#ffffff">We haven't got a fridge.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">That settles it.</font>

17:38.120 --> 17:41.240
<font color="#ffff00">Let's get you into</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the maternity home,</font>

17:41.240 --> 17:43.520
<font color="#ffff00">for cold compresses and bed rest.</font>

17:43.520 --> 17:45.040
<font color="#ffff00">We'll soon have you fighting fit.</font>

17:49.640 --> 17:51.320
<font color="#00ffff">Poor Mrs Lombardi.</font>

17:51.320 --> 17:53.680
<font color="#00ffff">She went into shock</font>
<font color="#00ffff">when we confirmed that pregnancy.</font>

17:53.680 --> 17:55.520
<font color="#00ffff">I had to make her blow in and out</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of a paper bag.</font>

17:55.520 --> 17:58.240
<font color="#00ffff">And she didn't even know</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it was twins at that point.</font>

17:58.240 --> 18:00.240
<font color="#ffffff">She kept skipping</font>
<font color="#ffffff">contraceptive pills</font>

18:00.240 --> 18:02.760
<font color="#ffffff">because she thought</font>
<font color="#ffffff">they were giving her pimples.</font>

18:02.760 --> 18:05.440
<font color="#ffff00">Apologies!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Apologies, Sister Julienne!</font>

18:05.440 --> 18:07.360
<font color="#ffff00">And of course, ladies.</font>

18:07.360 --> 18:08.880
<font color="#00ff00">Do please sit down.</font>

18:08.880 --> 18:11.960
<font color="#ffffff">PHONE RINGS</font>

18:11.960 --> 18:14.880
<font color="#00ffff">Did you get lost on your way home</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from the clinic, Sister Hilda?</font>

18:14.880 --> 18:16.040
<font color="#ffff00">Not remotely!</font>

18:16.040 --> 18:19.360
<font color="#ffff00">I did decide to take in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">some of my favourite sights</font>

18:19.360 --> 18:21.360
<font color="#ffff00">from my time in the East End</font>
<font color="#ffff00">during the Blitz.</font>

18:21.360 --> 18:23.840
<font color="#ffff00">But quite a lot of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the landmarks had vanished.</font>

18:23.840 --> 18:26.520
<font color="#00ffff">I think you'll find</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the Blitz had that effect.</font>

18:26.520 --> 18:27.680
<font color="#00ff00">Shall we say grace?</font>

18:27.680 --> 18:29.920
<font color="#00ff00">Nurse Anderson,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">perhaps you'd like to lead us.</font>

18:29.920 --> 18:31.280
<font color="#ffff00">Sorry to interrupt.</font>

18:32.560 --> 18:34.160
<font color="#ffff00">Has anyone seen Sister Monica Joan?</font>

18:34.160 --> 18:36.720
<font color="#ffff00">I just took her a plate</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of luncheon meat and an Eccles cake,</font>

18:36.720 --> 18:38.840
<font color="#ffff00">but she wasn't there,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">or in the bathroom.</font>

18:38.840 --> 18:40.520
<font color="#ffff00">And her bed is cold.</font>

18:43.320 --> 18:45.560
<font color="#00ffff">I hope she's all right.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">She can't be too far.</font>

18:45.560 --> 18:47.840
<font color="#00ff00">Nurse Franklin,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">go to the maternity home</font>

18:47.840 --> 18:49.640
<font color="#00ff00">and book in Mrs Lombardi.</font>

18:49.640 --> 18:52.440
<font color="#ffff00">Righto!</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Nurse Anderson and Nurse Dyer,</font>

18:52.440 --> 18:56.040
<font color="#00ff00">agree between yourselves</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the routes you wish to take.</font>

18:56.040 --> 18:57.560
<font color="#00ffff">I should've seen this coming.</font>

18:57.560 --> 19:00.360
<font color="#00ffff">She was in one of her fanciful moods</font>
<font color="#00ffff">this morning,</font>

19:00.360 --> 19:02.720
<font color="#00ffff">getting all morbid</font>
<font color="#00ffff">over those holdalls.</font>

19:02.720 --> 19:05.320
<font color="#ffffff">She's seemed so much better lately.</font>

19:05.320 --> 19:07.400
<font color="#ffff00">Her mental state</font>
<font color="#ffff00">has always been vulnerable</font>

19:07.400 --> 19:09.560
<font color="#ffff00">to infection and high fever.</font>

19:10.760 --> 19:13.400
<font color="#ffff00">I'm going inside,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to telephone the authorities.</font>

19:13.400 --> 19:16.960
<font color="#00ffff">And then, when I came back</font>
<font color="#00ffff">after fetching me dinner,</font>

19:16.960 --> 19:18.840
<font color="#00ffff">the last holdall was gone.</font>

19:18.840 --> 19:20.960
<font color="#00ffff">I should've smelt a rat then.</font>

19:20.960 --> 19:23.560
<font color="#ffff00">If Sister Monica Joan took the bag</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and went off with it,</font>

19:23.560 --> 19:26.160
<font color="#ffff00">do you suppose she thought</font>
<font color="#ffff00">she was on her way to work?</font>

19:26.160 --> 19:27.800
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, poor love.</font>

19:27.800 --> 19:29.800
<font color="#ffff00">You go and look</font>
<font color="#ffff00">down near the church</font>

19:29.800 --> 19:31.160
<font color="#ffff00">and in the churchyard.</font>

19:31.160 --> 19:33.720
<font color="#ffff00">Fred, you fetch your van and go</font>
<font color="#ffff00">up and down the Commercial Road.</font>

19:33.720 --> 19:35.720
<font color="#ffff00">And I'm going to follow</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my instincts.</font>

19:39.320 --> 19:42.200
<font color="#ffffff">When I open a filing cabinet,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I don't expect to find it</font>

19:42.200 --> 19:44.360
<font color="#ffffff">taken over by Lost Property.</font>

19:44.360 --> 19:50.400
<font color="#ffffff">Wallets under W, Odd Glove under O,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and a set of Dentures under D?</font>

19:50.400 --> 19:51.880
<font color="#ffffff">And what's all this?</font>

19:51.880 --> 19:53.120
<font color="#ffff00">Kiddies' toys.</font>

19:53.120 --> 19:54.560
<font color="#ffff00">They wouldn't fit under T.</font>

19:54.560 --> 19:55.600
<font color="#ffff00">Or K.</font>

19:55.600 --> 19:59.120
<font color="#ffffff">PHONE RINGS</font>

19:59.120 --> 20:01.480
<font color="#ffffff">Police station.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Sergeant Woolf speaking.</font>

20:01.480 --> 20:03.240
<font color="#00ffff">I'm calling from Nonnatus House.</font>

20:03.240 --> 20:05.880
<font color="#00ffff">It's an urgent</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and rather sensitive matter.</font>

20:05.880 --> 20:08.520
<font color="#ffffff">Sister, where Nonnatus House</font>
<font color="#ffffff">is concerned,</font>

20:08.520 --> 20:11.240
<font color="#ffffff">it's always an honour</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to be of service.</font>

20:16.440 --> 20:17.520
<font color="#ffff00">In a moment,</font>

20:17.520 --> 20:20.000
<font color="#ffff00">as you've rather conveniently</font>
<font color="#ffff00">settled on your side,</font>

20:20.000 --> 20:22.840
<font color="#ffff00">I'm going to apply the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">cold compress to your piles.</font>

20:22.840 --> 20:24.880
<font color="#ffff00">Possibly the nicest thing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that's ever slipped</font>

20:24.880 --> 20:26.200
<font color="#ffff00">under your covers.</font>

20:30.360 --> 20:32.320
<font color="#ffff00">And the treats just keep on coming!</font>

20:33.440 --> 20:35.280
<font color="#ffff00">I'd give Ladies' Choice</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a wide berth,</font>

20:35.280 --> 20:37.400
<font color="#ffff00">unless you want</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a blow by blow account</font>

20:37.400 --> 20:39.280
<font color="#ffff00">of Her Majesty's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">interesting condition.</font>

20:43.160 --> 20:44.560
<font color="#00ffff">Can I see her?</font>

20:44.560 --> 20:45.640
<font color="#ffff00">Who?</font>

20:45.640 --> 20:47.120
<font color="#00ffff">Her. She's my wife.</font>

20:47.120 --> 20:48.320
<font color="#ffffff">Clark!</font>

20:48.320 --> 20:49.680
<font color="#ffffff">Where are the kids?</font>

20:49.680 --> 20:51.160
<font color="#00ffff">They're with my mum.</font>

20:51.160 --> 20:53.040
<font color="#00ffff">She wanted to send</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you some veal cutlets,</font>

20:53.040 --> 20:57.520
<font color="#00ffff">I said no, but then I felt guilty</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so I brought you a custard slice.</font>

20:57.520 --> 20:59.160
<font color="#ffff00">You can stay for five minutes.</font>

20:59.160 --> 21:01.320
<font color="#ffff00">Give your wife one kiss,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and then leave.</font>

21:01.320 --> 21:05.400
<font color="#ffff00">It's after visiting hours,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">so I shall have my eye on you.</font>

21:15.600 --> 21:16.680
<font color="#00ffff">Sister, it's Valerie.</font>

21:18.960 --> 21:20.440
<font color="#00ffff">Valerie Dyer.</font>

21:21.720 --> 21:24.720
<font color="#00ffff">You must be tired, having walked</font>
<font color="#00ffff">all this way with that heavy bag.</font>

21:26.160 --> 21:27.880
<font color="#ffffff">Sister Monica Joan?</font>

21:28.880 --> 21:30.120
<font color="#ffffff">Sister?</font>

21:36.520 --> 21:38.600
<font color="#00ffff">Sister Monica Joan!</font>

21:38.600 --> 21:42.360
<font color="#00ffff">If you're anywhere near here,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">just call out to me!</font>

21:43.760 --> 21:46.840
<font color="#ffffff">DISTANT SHIP'S HORN SOUNDS</font>

21:48.680 --> 21:51.440
<font color="#ffffff">Did you hear that</font>
<font color="#ffffff">ship's horn just then?</font>

21:51.440 --> 21:54.760
<font color="#ffffff">It reminds me of when Dad</font>
<font color="#ffffff">used to be on the tug boats</font>

21:54.760 --> 21:56.280
<font color="#ffffff">when we were kids.</font>

22:00.280 --> 22:03.280
<font color="#ffffff">Be funny if this one worked on</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the river one day.</font>

22:03.280 --> 22:04.800
<font color="#ffffff">SHE VOMITS</font>

22:04.800 --> 22:06.480
<font color="#ffffff">Are you still not well?</font>

22:06.480 --> 22:08.480
<font color="#ffffff">I thought you said you were better!</font>

22:11.880 --> 22:13.240
<font color="#ffff00">Lesley...</font>

22:15.480 --> 22:17.360
<font color="#ffff00">..I'm not going to get better,</font>

22:17.360 --> 22:19.440
<font color="#ffff00">or be better until...</font>

22:19.440 --> 22:22.440
<font color="#ffff00">Something's happened down below.</font>

22:22.440 --> 22:23.800
<font color="#ffffff">What do you mean, "down below"?</font>

22:25.640 --> 22:27.480
<font color="#ffff00">I went to see a woman.</font>

22:28.880 --> 22:31.960
<font color="#ffff00">I had to! I was in the family way.</font>

22:31.960 --> 22:34.880
<font color="#ffff00">And until something comes away,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I still am.</font>

22:34.880 --> 22:37.400
<font color="#ffff00">I'm scared it hasn't worked.</font>

22:37.400 --> 22:39.240
<font color="#ffff00">I'm scared I won't lose it!</font>

22:39.240 --> 22:40.400
<font color="#ffffff">Are you bleeding?</font>

22:40.400 --> 22:42.040
<font color="#ffff00">A bit, but not enough.</font>

22:42.040 --> 22:44.040
<font color="#ffff00">I had it done two days ago.</font>

22:45.600 --> 22:47.200
<font color="#ffffff">You need to go to hospital, Cath.</font>

22:47.200 --> 22:48.560
<font color="#ffff00">I can't!</font>

22:48.560 --> 22:50.280
<font color="#ffff00">They'll send for the police.</font>

22:50.280 --> 22:52.120
<font color="#ffff00">It's against the law, Lesley!</font>

22:52.120 --> 22:53.480
<font color="#ffffff">Shhh.</font>

22:53.480 --> 22:55.440
<font color="#ffffff">It's all right. Sh, sh, sh.</font>

22:59.800 --> 23:01.520
<font color="#00ffff">Sister Monica Joan?</font>

