<font color="#ffff00">of irresponsibility.</font>

24:22.640 --> 24:25.080
<font color="#00ffff">There's a phone box</font>
<font color="#00ffff">round the corner.</font>

24:26.360 --> 24:29.240
<font color="#00ffff">Let's take a constitutional</font>
<font color="#00ffff">as far as there,</font>

24:29.240 --> 24:31.800
