<font color="#ffffff">What's done is done.</font>

33:32.520 --> 33:35.360
<font color="#ffffff">You have a new baby</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that needs your love,</font>

33:35.360 --> 33:37.520
<font color="#ffffff">your care, and your full attention.</font>

33:37.520 --> 33:40.360
<font color="#ffffff">You put everything else</font>
<font color="#ffffff">out of your mind.</font>

33:41.800 --> 33:46.000
<font color="#ffff00">What I saw in that bathroom</font>
<font color="#ffff00">will stay in my mind forever.</font>

33:54.920 --> 33:58.720
<font color="#00ffff">Now, there are a few crackles</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but they're quite faint.</font>

33:58.720 --> 34:01.760
<font color="#ffff00">You would doubtless</font>
