34:15.000 --> 34:18.480
<font color="#00ffff">Overall, our patient</font>
<font color="#00ffff">appears to be improving.</font>

34:21.920 --> 34:23.560
<font color="#ffff00">Morning, Mrs Lombardi.</font>

34:23.560 --> 34:25.120
<font color="#ffff00">What are you doing on your feet?</font>

