38:18.200 --> 38:20.480
<font color="#00ff00">The old lady at the desk</font>
<font color="#00ff00">said I could come through.</font>

38:20.480 --> 38:22.240
<font color="#00ffff">Is that another custard slice?</font>

38:22.240 --> 38:24.840
<font color="#00ff00">They didn't have none in today,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I bought her a cream horn.</font>

38:24.840 --> 38:26.920
<font color="#ffffff">He didn't bother that much</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with the other two!</font>

38:26.920 --> 38:28.160
<font color="#00ff00">Do you need a hand?</font>

38:28.160 --> 38:29.960
<font color="#ffff00">Everything's under control,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">thank you.</font>

38:29.960 --> 38:33.120
<font color="#00ffff">So much so, we've already</font>
<font color="#00ffff">written out the name bracelets!</font>

38:33.120 --> 38:35.920
<font color="#00ffff">Baby Lombardi one</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and two, and the date.</font>

38:42.360 --> 38:44.200
<font color="#00ffff">I'm sorry, Mr Lombardi.</font>

38:44.200 --> 38:46.560
<font color="#00ffff">But did you mean to take</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the cream horn with you?</font>

38:46.560 --> 38:47.960
<font color="#00ff00">Sorry.</font>

38:47.960 --> 38:50.480
<font color="#00ffff">We weren't going to let</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you see anything dreadful.</font>

38:50.480 --> 38:52.640
<font color="#00ffff">Nurse Crane was ready</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to shoo you away.</font>

38:52.640 --> 38:55.760
<font color="#00ff00">I'm a porter down Smithfield Market.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I'm not scared of blood or anything.</font>

38:57.720 --> 38:59.880
<font color="#00ff00">Will you make sure she gets it?</font>

38:59.880 --> 39:02.480
<font color="#00ff00">I don't want her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">running out of strength.</font>

39:02.480 --> 39:03.520
<font color="#00ffff">Of course.</font>

39:12.880 --> 39:14.040
<font color="#ffffff">Ow!</font>

39:14.040 --> 39:16.120
<font color="#ffffff">Ow, ow, ow.</font>

39:16.120 --> 39:18.000
<font color="#ffff00">That's what we want, lass.</font>

39:18.000 --> 39:21.120
<font color="#ffff00">The head coming slowly and steadily.</font>

39:22.960 --> 39:25.560
<font color="#00ffff">A head! </font><font color="#ffff00">There we are!</font>

39:25.560 --> 39:28.680
<font color="#ffffff">I'd forgotten what</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that bit felt like...</font>

39:28.680 --> 39:30.320
<font color="#ffff00">The body remembers.</font>

39:30.320 --> 39:33.080
<font color="#ffff00">And the body knows just what to do.</font>

39:34.200 --> 39:37.400
<font color="#00ffff">There's a lovely, warm towel</font>
<font color="#00ffff">waiting for baby now.</font>

39:39.640 --> 39:42.320
<font color="#ffffff">SHE STRAINS</font>

39:47.040 --> 39:51.000
<font color="#ffff00">And you have a daughter,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you clever girl!</font>

39:56.920 --> 39:59.360
<font color="#ffffff">BABY CRIES</font>

40:16.080 --> 40:18.840
<font color="#00ffff">Small but perfectly formed.</font>

40:21.040 --> 40:22.840
<font color="#00ff00">Now...</font>

40:24.760 --> 40:26.600
<font color="#00ff00">Now, you play nicely together</font>

40:26.600 --> 40:29.280
<font color="#00ff00">while I go and see to the letters</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in Daddy's surgery.</font>

40:34.000 --> 40:36.840
<font color="#ffffff">SHE GROANS</font>

40:44.360 --> 40:46.040
<font color="#00ffff">Bravo, Margaret.</font>

40:46.040 --> 40:48.280
<font color="#00ffff">Just rest for a moment.</font>

40:48.280 --> 40:50.560
<font color="#ffff00">Nurse Franklin, can you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">just pop along the corridor</font>

40:50.560 --> 40:53.000
<font color="#ffff00">and let Doctor know</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that Baby number two is breech?</font>

40:53.000 --> 40:55.480
<font color="#00ffff">I'll be back before you know it.</font>

40:56.880 --> 40:59.320
<font color="#ffffff">Does that mean baby's</font>
<font color="#ffffff">coming arse first?</font>

40:59.320 --> 41:01.080
<font color="#ffff00">Twins do it all the time.</font>

41:01.080 --> 41:04.240
<font color="#ffff00">But you might be more comfy</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on the birthing chair.</font>

41:07.000 --> 41:08.720
<font color="#ffffff">Just take a seat.</font>

41:11.280 --> 41:12.880
<font color="#ffffff">PHONE RINGS</font>

41:12.880 --> 41:14.320
<font color="#ffffff">Dr Turner's surgery.</font>

41:19.040 --> 41:20.880
<font color="#ffff00">Mother doesn't need our help.</font>

41:20.880 --> 41:24.040
<font color="#ffff00">She's doing magnificent work</font>
<font color="#ffff00">here, all on her own.</font>

41:26.080 --> 41:28.000
<font color="#ffff00">And here comes baby's bottom!</font>

41:29.640 --> 41:33.080
<font color="#ffff00">I'm going to wrap baby up</font>
<font color="#ffff00">nice and warm,</font>

41:33.080 --> 41:35.760
<font color="#ffff00">because we're going</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to have to concentrate</font>

41:35.760 --> 41:37.320
<font color="#ffff00">and take our time.</font>

41:48.160 --> 41:52.120
<font color="#ffff00">Gently push and then pant!</font>

41:52.120 --> 41:54.160
<font color="#ffff00">Short breaths.</font>

41:54.160 --> 41:56.720
<font color="#ffff00">That's the ticket.</font>

42:06.920 --> 42:08.720
<font color="#00ffff">Perfect work, Margaret.</font>

42:12.320 --> 42:14.040
<font color="#ffff00">Come along, young miss!</font>

42:14.040 --> 42:17.720
<font color="#ffff00">You've a sister waiting</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to wish you happy birthday!</font>

42:39.040 --> 42:40.840
<font color="#00ff00">Here you go!</font>

42:40.840 --> 42:43.280
<font color="#00ff00">Two beautiful girls.</font>

42:46.920 --> 42:48.120
<font color="#ffffff">Two!</font>

42:49.360 --> 42:50.440
<font color="#ffffff">Are they identical?</font>

42:50.440 --> 42:54.480
<font color="#00ffff">The afterbirth can give us a clue,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but only time will tell sometimes.</font>

42:54.480 --> 42:57.280
<font color="#00ff00">They're both absolutely</font>
<font color="#00ff00">gorgeous all the same.</font>

42:59.080 --> 43:01.840
<font color="#ffffff">CHILDREN GIGGLE</font>

43:12.440 --> 43:13.640
<font color="#00ff00">Shelagh!</font>

43:27.880 --> 43:29.480
<font color="#ffff00">Doctor Turner?</font>

43:29.480 --> 43:32.240
<font color="#ffff00">May I ask for your opinion?</font>

43:32.240 --> 43:34.760
<font color="#ffff00">I believe I can hear</font>
<font color="#ffff00">another heartbeat.</font>

43:36.840 --> 43:38.400
<font color="#00ffff">Third baby?</font>

43:41.040 --> 43:43.440
<font color="#00ff00">Yes. We need to get her on the bed.</font>

43:43.440 --> 43:45.480
<font color="#ffffff">SHE WAILS</font>

43:45.480 --> 43:48.960
<font color="#ffff00">It's all right, it's all right.</font>

43:50.280 --> 43:53.880
<font color="#00ff00">Never, ever, go through</font>
<font color="#00ff00">those doors into the rooms</font>

43:53.880 --> 43:57.520
<font color="#00ff00">where the poorly mummies and the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">babies are, do you hear me?</font>

43:57.520 --> 44:00.400
<font color="#00ff00">I'm very disappointed</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in both of you,</font>

44:00.400 --> 44:01.600
<font color="#00ff00">but especially Angela,</font>

44:01.600 --> 44:04.840
<font color="#00ff00">because you're a big girl</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and you should know better.</font>

44:08.720 --> 44:12.640
<font color="#00ffff">Shelagh said there were three poles.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">When I checked, there were only two.</font>

44:12.640 --> 44:16.040
<font color="#ffff00">It must have shifted,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to lie behind the others.</font>

44:16.040 --> 44:19.840
<font color="#00ff00">Now it's shifted again,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">because it's got the room to move.</font>

44:19.840 --> 44:22.200
<font color="#00ff00">And it's transverse.</font>

44:22.200 --> 44:24.680
<font color="#ffffff">I can't do it again.</font>

44:24.680 --> 44:28.320
<font color="#00ff00">You are going to get all the help</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that we can give you.</font>

44:28.320 --> 44:31.360
<font color="#00ff00">Starting by turning this</font>
<font color="#00ff00">baby around.</font>

44:46.440 --> 44:48.440
<font color="#00ff00">This baby needs to be delivered.</font>

44:48.440 --> 44:50.440
<font color="#00ff00">The heart rate is very, very rapid.</font>

44:54.560 --> 44:56.960
<font color="#00ffff">We need the obstetric</font>
<font color="#00ffff">flying squad urgently.</font>

44:56.960 --> 44:58.800
<font color="#00ffff">You were right. Triplets.</font>

44:58.800 --> 45:00.680
<font color="#ffff00">Sit there and don't move.</font>

45:06.840 --> 45:10.280
<font color="#00ff00">I've located the head and the back,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but I can't get it to turn.</font>

45:10.280 --> 45:11.640
<font color="#ffff00">Shall I try?</font>

45:11.640 --> 45:13.920
<font color="#00ff00">Yes. I'll prep for forceps.</font>

45:15.960 --> 45:18.600
<font color="#00ffff">You've done so much hard work.</font>

45:18.600 --> 45:20.720
<font color="#00ffff">You leave this to us now.</font>

45:35.080 --> 45:36.640
<font color="#ffff00">I think it's engaging.</font>

45:37.720 --> 45:40.480
<font color="#00ff00">Waters have broken,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and there's meconium.</font>

45:42.320 --> 45:43.920
<font color="#ffffff">What does that mean?</font>

45:43.920 --> 45:47.080
<font color="#00ffff">Just that in a minute,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">we'll be telling you to push again.</font>

45:47.080 --> 45:49.520
<font color="#00ffff">Everything's in hand, lass.</font>

45:49.520 --> 45:51.240
<font color="#00ffff">Don't worry.</font>

46:06.200 --> 46:08.040
<font color="#00ff00">Pudendal block given.</font>

46:17.120 --> 46:18.400
<font color="#00ff00">First blade.</font>

46:22.280 --> 46:23.440
<font color="#00ff00">Second blade.</font>

46:23.440 --> 46:25.480
<font color="#00ffff">Push. You push now.</font>

46:25.480 --> 46:27.840
<font color="#00ffff">We'll soon have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">everything to rights.</font>

46:40.760 --> 46:42.000
<font color="#00ff00">Baby's out.</font>

46:43.600 --> 46:45.240
<font color="#00ffff">Well done.</font>

46:45.240 --> 46:46.680
<font color="#00ff00">Another girl.</font>

46:47.760 --> 46:49.480
<font color="#00ffff">Well done, lass.</font>

46:52.120 --> 46:53.960
<font color="#00ffff">You did so well.</font>

47:00.480 --> 47:02.280
<font color="#ffffff">Can I see her?</font>

47:02.280 --> 47:04.400
<font color="#00ffff">Two ticks, I promise.</font>

47:08.400 --> 47:10.280
<font color="#ffffff">Is she all right?</font>

47:24.040 --> 47:27.400
<font color="#00ffff">Little lady just needs</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a bit of a rub down.</font>

47:55.520 --> 47:57.080
<font color="#ffffff">KNOCK ON DOOR</font>

47:57.080 --> 47:59.400
<font color="#00ff00">Flying squad! </font><font color="#00ffff">Hold on a moment.</font>

48:09.680 --> 48:12.480
<font color="#ffffff">BABY CRIES</font>

48:23.560 --> 48:25.880
<font color="#ffffff">Can I hold her?</font>

48:27.280 --> 48:29.040
<font color="#00ffff">Baby's still very weak.</font>

48:30.520 --> 48:32.080
<font color="#00ffff">Not just yet.</font>

48:35.240 --> 48:37.520
<font color="#ffffff">And did the lady</font>
<font color="#ffffff">give you any information</font>

48:37.520 --> 48:40.240
<font color="#ffffff">about the procedure she'd undergone?</font>

48:40.240 --> 48:43.760
<font color="#ffffff">Any indication, at all,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of the name of the practitioner?</font>

48:43.760 --> 48:45.400
<font color="#00ffff">At that point, it didn't matter.</font>

48:46.520 --> 48:48.920
<font color="#00ffff">I just knew something</font>
<font color="#00ffff">very distressing</font>

48:48.920 --> 48:50.240
<font color="#00ffff">was going to happen to her,</font>

48:50.240 --> 48:52.800
<font color="#00ffff">and that there might be</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a haemorrhage afterwards.</font>

48:52.800 --> 48:54.560
<font color="#00ffff">She wasn't a criminal, Sergeant.</font>

48:54.560 --> 48:56.280
<font color="#00ffff">She was my patient.</font>

48:59.040 --> 49:01.200
<font color="#ffffff">I want to try feeding them myself.</font>

49:01.200 --> 49:04.280
<font color="#00ffff">I'm afraid baby number three</font>
<font color="#00ffff">will have artificial milk</font>

49:04.280 --> 49:06.200
<font color="#00ffff">while she's at St Cuthbert's.</font>

49:08.680 --> 49:10.680
<font color="#ffffff">I need someone to tell my husband.</font>

49:11.920 --> 49:14.280
<font color="#ffffff">They might have to take</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the gas and air.</font>

49:14.280 --> 49:16.280
<font color="#00ffff">I'm off duty soon.</font>

49:16.280 --> 49:19.200
<font color="#00ffff">I don't mind passing on</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the glad tidings.</font>

49:19.200 --> 49:20.560
<font color="#ffffff">Thanks, nurse.</font>

49:21.760 --> 49:23.600
<font color="#ffffff">He'll be down the Black Sail.</font>

49:27.040 --> 49:29.640
<font color="#ffff00">The woman won't see</font>
<font color="#ffff00">anyone in her own home.</font>

49:29.640 --> 49:32.680
<font color="#ffff00">You have to meet her friend,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and the friend takes the money,</font>

49:32.680 --> 49:34.960
<font color="#ffff00">and gives you the address.</font>

49:34.960 --> 49:36.800
<font color="#ffffff">But you don't know what it is?</font>

49:41.080 --> 49:43.720
<font color="#ffff00">I don't want this</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to happen to anybody else.</font>

49:43.720 --> 49:46.840
<font color="#ffff00">But those women,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">they'll be out there now,</font>

49:46.840 --> 49:48.640
<font color="#ffff00">looking for more customers.</font>

49:48.640 --> 49:51.640
<font color="#ffff00">And there will always be customers.</font>

49:57.800 --> 50:01.320
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHTER AND CHATTER</font>

50:13.240 --> 50:14.840
<font color="#00ff00">Drink, dear?</font>

50:14.840 --> 50:18.120
<font color="#00ff00">I can't have a Nonnatun coming</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in here and standing empty handed.</font>

50:19.480 --> 50:21.720
<font color="#00ffff">I'd like an orange juice, please.</font>

50:21.720 --> 50:22.920
<font color="#00ff00">Nothing but the best.</font>

50:22.920 --> 50:25.520
<font color="#00ff00">I shall open a fresh tin. </font><font color="#00ffff">Ooh!</font>

50:30.920 --> 50:33.680
<font color="#ffffff">CHEERING</font>

50:35.320 --> 50:38.360
<font color="#ffffff"># Daisy, daisy</font>

50:38.360 --> 50:41.640
<font color="#ffffff"># Give me your answer do... #</font>

50:41.640 --> 50:43.400
<font color="#ffff00">I've got five kids.</font>

50:43.400 --> 50:45.000
<font color="#ffff00">Five.</font>

50:45.000 --> 50:47.600
<font color="#ffff00">It was hard enough getting</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my head around twins,</font>

50:47.600 --> 50:49.040
<font color="#ffff00">but triplets?!</font>

50:49.040 --> 50:50.520
<font color="#ffff00">I've never even seen triplets!</font>

50:50.520 --> 50:53.440
<font color="#ffff00">I don't think there's any triplets</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in Poplar. </font><font color="#00ff00">You clever boy!</font>

50:53.440 --> 50:55.200
<font color="#00ffff">It's not unheard of.</font>

50:55.200 --> 50:58.320
<font color="#00ffff">But often, in the past,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">they wouldn't have survived.</font>

50:58.320 --> 51:01.000
<font color="#00ffff">But yours will all thrive,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">even the poorly one,</font>

51:01.000 --> 51:02.720
<font color="#00ffff">once she's out of her incubator.</font>

51:02.720 --> 51:04.240
<font color="#ffff00">Poorly? How poorly is she?</font>

51:04.240 --> 51:05.680
<font color="#00ffff">She's the smallest of the three.</font>

51:05.680 --> 51:08.080
<font color="#00ffff">She inhaled</font>
<font color="#00ffff">some unpleasant substances</font>

51:08.080 --> 51:09.840
<font color="#00ffff">while she was in the womb,</font>

51:09.840 --> 51:12.080
<font color="#00ffff">and she needs</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a little help breathing.</font>

51:12.080 --> 51:14.640
<font color="#ffff00">What made that happen?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Her birth was traumatic enough</font>

51:14.640 --> 51:16.920
<font color="#00ffff">that she went into a state</font>
<font color="#00ffff">known as foetal distress.</font>

51:16.920 --> 51:19.520
<font color="#ffff00">Distress? Was she scared?</font>

51:19.520 --> 51:21.000
<font color="#00ffff">Panicked, perhaps.</font>

51:21.000 --> 51:22.400
<font color="#00ffff">Alarmed.</font>

51:22.400 --> 51:25.480
<font color="#00ffff">But she wouldn't have been able</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to name what she was feeling.</font>

51:25.480 --> 51:29.760
<font color="#00ffff">Sometimes even grown adults</font>
<font color="#00ffff">can't name the things</font>

51:29.760 --> 51:31.200
<font color="#00ffff">that scare them the most.</font>

51:31.200 --> 51:34.440
<font color="#ffff00">Is anyone with her now?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Margaret's too unwell to go to her.</font>

51:37.360 --> 51:39.600
<font color="#ffff00">She needs to be with family.</font>

52:17.680 --> 52:19.280
<font color="#ffff00">Hello, bambino.</font>

52:23.080 --> 52:24.640
<font color="#ffff00">I'm your dad.</font>

52:25.720 --> 52:29.560
<font color="#ffff00">You've got brothers and sisters.</font>

52:33.880 --> 52:36.320
<font color="#ffff00">You've got a really brave mum.</font>

52:37.560 --> 52:39.640
<font color="#ffff00">Almost as brave as you are.</font>

52:41.640 --> 52:43.840
<font color="#ffff00">Can you make do with me for now?</font>

52:54.320 --> 52:56.600
<font color="#ffffff">They said they</font>
<font color="#ffffff">don't want you leaving yet!</font>

52:56.600 --> 52:58.920
<font color="#00ffff">They can't stop me</font>
<font color="#00ffff">discharging myself.</font>

52:58.920 --> 53:01.840
<font color="#00ffff">When I'm better, I'm moving up west.</font>

53:01.840 --> 53:04.280
<font color="#00ffff">I'm rearranging that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">appointment with the agency.</font>

53:04.280 --> 53:06.080
<font color="#00ffff">I'm going to start again.</font>

53:06.080 --> 53:08.520
<font color="#ffffff">Will you talk to the police</font>
<font color="#ffffff">before you go?</font>

53:08.520 --> 53:11.440
<font color="#00ffff">Don't you understand?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I want it to be over, Lesley!</font>

53:11.440 --> 53:13.800
<font color="#00ffff">I want it to be in the past!</font>

53:15.040 --> 53:17.200
<font color="#00ffff">The past begins when I walk away.</font>

53:19.760 --> 53:21.160
<font color="#00ffff">The shame...</font>

53:21.160 --> 53:23.960
<font color="#00ffff">..I'll carry with me</font>
<font color="#00ffff">everywhere I go.</font>

53:27.840 --> 53:29.960
<font color="#ffffff">This needs new batteries.</font>

53:29.960 --> 53:32.120
<font color="#ffffff">It's just not loud enough!</font>

53:32.120 --> 53:35.000
<font color="#ffffff">There'll be a news-flash</font>
<font color="#ffffff">when Her Majesty's baby's born</font>

53:35.000 --> 53:36.560
<font color="#ffffff">and I can't afford to miss it.</font>

53:36.560 --> 53:39.720
<font color="#00ffff">There'll be a 41-gun salute</font>
<font color="#00ffff">all down the Thames</font>

53:39.720 --> 53:43.120
<font color="#00ffff">when she drops that sprog. You won't</font>
<font color="#00ffff">need batteries to hear that!</font>

53:46.680 --> 53:49.000
<font color="#ffff00">I crave your indulgence.</font>

53:53.400 --> 53:59.240
<font color="#ffff00">News has come to me that this</font>
<font color="#ffff00">object fuelled my delusions,</font>

53:59.240 --> 54:02.040
<font color="#ffff00">when I was afflicted with pyrexia.</font>

54:02.040 --> 54:05.480
<font color="#ffff00">It is best that you destroy it.</font>

54:06.680 --> 54:08.400
<font color="#ffffff">She's had it!</font>

54:08.400 --> 54:10.120
<font color="#ffffff">The Queen's had the baby!</font>

54:10.120 --> 54:12.680
<font color="#00ffff">Just leave that with me.</font>

54:12.680 --> 54:15.040
<font color="#ffffff">It's a prince.</font>

54:15.040 --> 54:16.760
<font color="#ffffff">It's a prince!</font>

54:16.760 --> 54:19.720
<font color="#ffffff">The Queen's had a boy!</font>

54:19.720 --> 54:22.400
<font color="#ffffff">The Queen's had a boy!!</font>

54:25.200 --> 54:27.400
<font color="#ffffff"># I like it</font>

54:27.400 --> 54:29.120
<font color="#ffffff"># I like it</font>

54:29.120 --> 54:31.160
<font color="#ffffff"># I like the way you run</font>

54:31.160 --> 54:34.160
<font color="#ffffff"># Your fingers through my hair</font>

54:34.160 --> 54:36.120
<font color="#ffffff"># And I like the way</font>

54:36.120 --> 54:38.040
<font color="#ffffff"># You tickle my chin</font>

54:38.040 --> 54:39.320
<font color="#ffffff"># And I like the way</font>

54:39.320 --> 54:40.960
<font color="#ffffff"># You let me come in</font>

54:40.960 --> 54:43.800
<font color="#ffffff"># When your mama ain't there</font>

54:45.160 --> 54:48.560
<font color="#ffffff"># I like it, I like it</font>

54:48.560 --> 54:50.480
<font color="#ffffff"># I like the words you say</font>

54:50.480 --> 54:53.520
<font color="#ffffff"># And all the things you do</font>

54:54.640 --> 54:57.440
<font color="#ffffff"># And I like the way</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you straighten my tie</font>

54:57.440 --> 55:00.520
<font color="#ffffff"># And I like the way</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you're winkin' your eye</font>

55:00.520 --> 55:03.160
<font color="#ffffff"># And I know I like you</font>

55:03.160 --> 55:06.680
<font color="#ffffff"># You know I like you</font>

55:08.240 --> 55:10.120
<font color="#ffffff"># Do that again</font>

55:11.400 --> 55:14.400
<font color="#ffffff"># You're driving me insane</font>

55:14.400 --> 55:17.240
<font color="#ffffff"># Kiss me once more</font>

55:17.240 --> 55:20.560
<font color="#ffffff"># That's another thing</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I like you for</font>

55:24.080 --> 55:26.520
<font color="#ffffff"># Are you liking it too? #</font>

55:30.040 --> 55:32.000
<font color="#ffffff">Scum on the water.</font>

55:32.000 --> 55:35.160
<font color="#ffffff">One forgets, living</font>
<font color="#ffffff">on the South Coast for so long.</font>

55:35.160 --> 55:37.640
<font color="#ffff00">I can't remember</font>
<font color="#ffff00">when I last noticed.</font>

55:41.480 --> 55:45.280
<font color="#ffffff">I've spoken with Sister Frances</font>
<font color="#ffffff">about the abortion case.</font>

55:45.280 --> 55:48.280
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry her first week</font>
<font color="#ffff00">here's been marred by this.</font>

55:48.280 --> 55:50.040
<font color="#ffffff">Lives are marred by this.</font>

55:50.040 --> 55:51.600
<font color="#ffffff">And they're marred everywhere.</font>

55:52.680 --> 55:54.280
<font color="#ffffff">I was once first on the scene</font>

55:54.280 --> 55:56.880
<font color="#ffffff">after a woman took</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a screwdriver to herself.</font>

55:56.880 --> 55:59.960
<font color="#ffffff">Afterwards, every time</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I cycled past her house,</font>

55:59.960 --> 56:04.000
<font color="#ffffff">I used to think, "But there</font>
<font color="#ffffff">were roses round the door."</font>

56:04.000 --> 56:07.000
<font color="#ffff00">There are women all over</font>
<font color="#ffff00">this district who "help"</font>

56:07.000 --> 56:09.040
<font color="#ffff00">other women all the time.</font>

56:09.040 --> 56:10.680
<font color="#ffff00">They think of themselves as we do.</font>

56:10.680 --> 56:12.400
<font color="#ffff00">No-one will name them because,</font>

56:12.400 --> 56:15.840
<font color="#ffff00">for every woman who finds herself</font>
<font color="#ffff00">maimed, or dead,</font>

56:15.840 --> 56:21.120
<font color="#ffff00">there are a dozen others who</font>
<font color="#ffff00">quietly get the desired result.</font>

56:21.120 --> 56:23.800
<font color="#ffffff">But if no-one speaks out,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">where will it end?</font>

56:23.800 --> 56:25.720
<font color="#ffff00">It will end where it always ends.</font>

56:25.720 --> 56:27.120
<font color="#ffff00">In silence.</font>

56:33.560 --> 56:37.360
<font color="#ffffff">There are too many things</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of which we do not speak.</font>

56:37.360 --> 56:40.120
<font color="#ffffff">Too many secrets.</font>

56:40.120 --> 56:41.840
<font color="#ffffff">Too much shame.</font>

56:43.120 --> 56:46.960
<font color="#ffffff">But perhaps we are cleaner,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">brighter,</font>

56:46.960 --> 56:49.880
<font color="#ffffff">more polished versions of ourselves</font>

56:49.880 --> 56:52.840
<font color="#ffffff">more often than we think.</font>

56:57.680 --> 57:00.640
<font color="#ffffff">When we gaze outward and not inward,</font>

57:00.640 --> 57:04.160
<font color="#ffffff">when we are open, not closed.</font>

57:06.560 --> 57:09.520
<font color="#ffffff">Not everything is possible,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">but there is hope.</font>

57:11.040 --> 57:13.120
<font color="#ffffff">When the light shines in...</font>

57:14.520 --> 57:17.160
<font color="#ffffff">..hope is another chapter.</font>

57:17.160 --> 57:19.600
<font color="#ffffff">Hope is what comes next.</font>

57:23.280 --> 57:24.640
<font color="#00ffff">Flora!</font>

57:24.640 --> 57:26.480
<font color="#00ffff">Flora, keep your eyes open!</font>

57:26.480 --> 57:28.280
<font color="#ffffff">Could I have given</font>
<font color="#ffffff">this to my children?</font>

57:28.280 --> 57:29.320
<font color="#ffff00">What will become of me?</font>

57:29.320 --> 57:30.640
<font color="#ffff00">I know nowhere else.</font>

57:30.640 --> 57:33.520
<font color="#ffffff">This isn't your home any more,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Clarice, it is a prison.</font>

57:33.520 --> 57:35.000
<font color="#00ffff">Vote Violet Buckle!</font>

57:35.000 --> 57:37.480
<font color="#ffff00">I don't put my cross in the box</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for any old rubbish!</font>

57:37.480 --> 57:39.720
<font color="#00ffff">Well, it seems like an awful</font>
<font color="#00ffff">lot of bother to go to</font>

57:39.720 --> 57:41.200
<font color="#00ffff">just to put an X in a box.</font>

